description: Get file link to download/create shipping document. You have to call v2.logistics.create_shipping_document to create a new shipping document first.

parameters.name: partner_id
parameters.description: Partner ID is assigned when application is successful. Required for all requests.

parameters.name: timestamp
parameters.description: This is to indicate the timestamp of the request. Required for all requests. Expires in 5 minutes

parameters.name: access_token
parameters.description: The token for API usage, using to identify your permission to the api. Valid for multiple use and expire in 4 hours

parameters.name: shipping_document_type
parameters.description: The type of shipping document. Available values: NORMAL_AIR_WAYBILL, THERMAL_AIR_WAYBILL

parameters.name: booking_sn
parameters.description: Shipper's unique identifier for a booking
